  <trk>
    <name>Mule Track Gries Pass</name>
    <desc>The mule track is a scenic ascent along a mule path from the Rhone Valley up to the remote pass summit at the Italian border. The hike combines history, pristine landscapes, and a pioneering ecological project.</desc>
